node.text: Together, Make-A-Wish and @MarvelStudios helped bring Seth’s wish to life! Seth, who’s now 20 years old, was inspired by his wish experience and is currently studying audio production in college as he prepares for a future in the sound industry. 🎥  @MakeAWishGA #DisneyWishes
